{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-warm-up-introducing-yourself-basics/task-8","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"es-a1-warm-up-introducing-yourself-basics","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U Hispaniji, broj 20 je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veinte</span>.</p>\n<p>Kada generišete brojeve od 21 do 29, reči se malo menjaju. <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinte</span> menja se u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veinti-</span> (uklanja se poslednji deo <span class=\"highlighted-text\">e</span>), zatim se spaja sa sledećim brojem. Primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinti</span> + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">dos</span> (mbili) = <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veintidós</span> (22)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinti</span> + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">cinco</span> (pet) = <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veinticinco</span> (25)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinti</span> + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ocho</span> (nane) = <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veintiocho</span> (28)</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinticinco años</span> - Dvadeset pet godina.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio odgovor na pitanje ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-warm-up-introducing-yourself-basics/task-8"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koja je to starost koju Mateo pominje?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinticinco años</span></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintiocho años</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ovo znači \"dvadeset osam godina\". Mateo kaže da je broj ispod dvadeset osam.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinte años</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ovo znači \"dvadeset godina\". Broj koji Mateo kaže je veći.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veintidós años</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ovo znači \"dvadeset dve godine\". Broj koji Mateo kaže je veći.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":1}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"interview-room3.png","characters":[{"character":"Mateo","position":{"x":50,"y":18,"z":1.5},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ES_A1_spanish_introducing_yourself_vocabulary.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":27.2,"finishTimestamp":29.6},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Mateo","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Mateo","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":3.4,"dialogue":{"text":"Veinticinco años","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Mateo","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":3.9,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 8","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-warm-up-introducing-yourself-basics","dashedName":"task-8","certification":"a1-professional-spanish","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","chapter":"es-a1-chapter-greetings-and-introductions","module":"es-a1-module-introducing-yourself","block":"es-a1-warm-up-introducing-yourself-basics","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-warm-up-introducing-yourself-basics/task-9","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-warm-up-introducing-y